  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/4cdfe3e7fe2e9ec6687d6b6f78464ef1.avif?t=1760712740\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras_big/4cdfe3e7fe2e9ec6687d6b6f78464ef1.avif?t=1760712740 width=800 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Some days, you just need to fly. Soar offers something rare, a space designed for your peace of mind. Transform into a dragon and glide through beautiful floating islands where the only goal is clearing your mind and unwinding.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/8d28c36399244c80cc6453f5fc6c41f6.avif?t=1760712740\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras_big/8d28c36399244c80cc6453f5fc6c41f6.avif?t=1760712740 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/98cbb23e6ffee820330d16b649fa4d1c.avif?t=1760712740\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras_big/98cbb23e6ffee820330d16b649fa4d1c.avif?t=1760712740 width=800 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tasneem is a realm of floating islands touched by an ancient corruption. As Nur, you have the gift of flight and the ability to bring gentle healing to wounded lands. There's no rushing and no combat, just the pure joy of flight and the satisfaction of bringing beauty back to forgotten places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/c4e5a46267a087e9b2a6ffa491155e17.poster.avif?t=1760712740\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/c4e5a46267a087e9b2a6ffa491155e17.webm?t=1760712740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/c4e5a46267a087e9b2a6ffa491155e17.mp4?t=1760712740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What Players Say:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"I played the game off and on before release and I really enjoyed the vibe of the game...\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"...for the most part, it's a chill and relaxing exploration game.\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"I love flying around! I wanna see where this game goes!\"</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Award-Winning Adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>SOAR: Pillars of Tasneem</i> was honored as a \"Best in Play\" winner at GDC 2022, recognizing its breathtaking world, innovative flight mechanics, and immersive atmosphere. Take to the skies and experience an <strong>award-winning</strong> journey for yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/fc8e71e61d26693dcf59eb3cbd143357.poster.avif?t=1760712740\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/fc8e71e61d26693dcf59eb3cbd143357.webm?t=1760712740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/fc8e71e61d26693dcf59eb3cbd143357.mp4?t=1760712740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/4ef30d95976184a3e2339862b9bb000f.avif?t=1760712740\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras_big/4ef30d95976184a3e2339862b9bb000f.avif?t=1760712740 width=800 height=107 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience the Pure Joy of Flight: </strong>Soar freely across the open skies: ride the wind, carve through canyons, and dance between floating ruins. Whether you seek relaxing exploration or high-speed aerial thrills, the sky is yours to command.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Vast & Vibrant Open World: </strong>Tasneem is alive with wonders waiting to be discovered. Explore sunlit archipelagos, lush forests, ancient temples, and towering pillars, each with their own mysteries and history.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gentle Goals, No Pressure: </strong>Light collection tasks and trials give your flight purpose without creating stress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aesthetic, Meditative Vibes: </strong>SOAR is more than just an adventure, it’s a wholesome, relaxing experience. Immerse yourself in the beauty of the world, and let your mind wander as you glide through the skies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Your Own Way: </strong>Whether you have 15 minutes or 2 hours, Soar adapts to your schedule, perfect for unwinding after work, clearing your mind, or finding focus.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An Immersive Soundscape: </strong>Let the world pull you in with a stunning, dynamic soundtrack that ebbs and flows with your journey. Every moment in SOAR is accompanied by an enchanting atmosphere of music and sound.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/7220a9a989542084d9ce0e790183dfbd.poster.avif?t=1760712740\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/7220a9a989542084d9ce0e790183dfbd.webm?t=1760712740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/7220a9a989542084d9ce0e790183dfbd.mp4?t=1760712740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/9346487743e482683bd07522f1037581.avif?t=1760712740\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras_big/9346487743e482683bd07522f1037581.avif?t=1760712740 width=800 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Had a stressful day? Let the wind guide you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looking for a challenge? Push your flight to the limit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need something to pair with a podcast? Enjoy effortless, beautiful exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>SOAR: Pillars of Tasneem</i>, the sky is not just a setting: it’s a feeling, a journey, and a world waiting to be discovered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Add <i>SOAR: Pillars of Tasneem</i> to your wishlist and prepare to take flight!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras/7e0568b057b22e1cefd8f2d300b85414.avif?t=1760712740\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513030/extras_big/7e0568b057b22e1cefd8f2d300b85414.avif?t=1760712740 width=800 height=106 /></span></p>",
